<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Lomo Blog - About</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/img/favicon.ico" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/aboutPage.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css" />
    <!-- Bootstrap css -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <!-- Fontawesome CDN -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.4/css/all.css"
      integrity="sha384-DyZ88mC6Up2uqS4h/KRgHuoeGwBcD4Ng9SiP4dIRy0EXTlnuz47vAwmeGwVChigm"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />

    <%- include("partials/googleAnalytics") %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>
    <!--  -->
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xl-8 col-sm-12 leftSide">
          <h2>About lomo blog</h2>
          <div id="imgContainer">
            <img
              src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2015/06/08/15/02/pug-801826_960_720.jpg"
              alt="lomo blog"
            />
          </div>
          <p>
            This project was an exercice of the Hack Academy Bootcamp. It is a
            server side render web page and a blog about lomitos.
          </p>
          <p>Technologies used in ths web page:</p>
          <ol>
            <li>Node.Js</li>
            <li>Express</li>
            <li>EJS</li>
            <li>Bootstrap</li>
            <li>Passport js: Facebook login, Google login</li>
            <li>MVC architecture model</li>
            <li>Supabase and postgres for database</li>
            <li>Deployed in Vercel</li>
          </ol>
          <p>In this page there are 4 Roles</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Lector: Can see articles and make comments.</li>
            <li>
              Writer: Can see articles and make comments. Also make CRUD of his
              own articles.
            </li>
            <li>
              Editor: Can make CRUD of own articles and just edit other
              articles. He can not delete articles of other person.
            </li>
            <li>Admin: Can make CRUD of any entity, even Users</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xl-4 col-sm-12 rightSide">
          <div>
            <a class="btn btn-danger" aria-current="page" href="/generate"
              ><i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Generate</a
            >
            <p>
              Populate the web page with lomo articles and with an Admin
              account. Admin credentials: <br />
              User: admin@admin.com
              <br />
              Pass: admin
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" aria-current="page" href="/api/articles"
              ><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Json</a
            >
            <p>See all the articles of this page in JSON format.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%- include("partials/footer") %>

    <!-- JS bootstrap -->
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
